{
  "stem": "5103.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody had lost their schooling, so we were all sitting in-- in second class, all on one level.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Big boys, little children, and everybody together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said-- my parents said, look you've got to do your best, because we want you to do well.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I went, and I tried to do it, and I did it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I did two classes every year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In other words, when I did, like, first and second, third and fourth, you know, like that, fifth and sixth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then that was very good, because then I was supposed to go to high school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was nearly 13 when I was supposed to go to high school, and I made it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Normally it's 12, but I made it, which was good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, we had a headmaster that was an antisemite.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "After all this, we discovered there was one headmaster in that school that was a terrible antisemite.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he had decided that [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Corrie ?] Swaab was not going to high school, because she had skipped too many classes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She'd done too many in the three years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I did three years when normal people do six.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my parents said, but she has sat for the test, and she will go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She will go to high school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She's done enough, had enough trouble, that she's not going to now go backwards, and you hold her back, because it's not fair.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they said-- he said no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father said, then she will sit for another test under the government, and I will make sure that she will get that test.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my father, by that time, wasn't taking any more nonsense.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He'd had enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
